<plot>The Ice Cream Social updates the classic variety show format, blends in aspects of the talk show format, and envelops the whole in comedy. Combining elements of Laugh-In, American Bandstand, Ed Sullivan, and Charlie Rose, the Ice Cream Social is a weekly hour-long party with an ensemble cast of regulars and an ever-changing array of guests and performers.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?565902</url></doc>
